record_data.record_title: KU Concurrence Certificate
record_data.record_plain_text:
CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE
This is to certify that Kentucky Utilities Company (KU), a regulated electric utility based in Lexington, Kentucky, assents to and concurs to the baseline tariff described below, which Louisville Gas and Electric Company (LG&E) has filed. KU and LG&E are affiliates. KU hereby files this Certificate of Concurrence in lieu of filing of the specified tariff.
JOINT PRO FORMA OPEN ACCESS TRANSMISSION TARIFF: LOUISVILLE GAS AND ELECTRIC COMPANY AND KENTUCKY UTILITIES COMPANY
Kentucky Utilities Company By its duly authorized official
/s/ Paul W. Thompson ______________________________________ Paul W. Thompson Senior Vice President, Energy Services
Dated this 21st day of June 2010
